Package: ludwig
Title: Simulating and Estimating Undirected Binary Networks Using the
    Pseudolikelihood Method
Version: 0.0.2
Authors@R: c(person("Georg", "Hosoya", email = "hosoya@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
            person("Maximilian", "Bee", email= "r.maximilian.bee@gmail.com", role = c("ctb")))
Description: The package provides some basic functions for simulating,
    estimating and plotting binary networks. The estimation function is using the
    'glmnet' package. The plotting function is using the 'qgraph' package.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5)
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    glmnet (>= 2.0.5),
    qgraph (>= 1.3.4),
    mcmcplots (>= 0.4.2),
    coda (>= 0.19-1)
Suggests:
    rjags (>= 4.0)
SystemRequirements: jags 4.2.0
